<plot>Mary Williams doesn't have much time to live. An unexpected man arrives at her door and demands to be let in. He pulls a gun and she opens the door. The man explains to her that he was once one of her customers and he contracted AIDS from her. He is now here to kill her. But the man is not a killer, and he realizes that facing himself and the ones he loves isn't going to be easy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?572179</url></doc>
